sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User prompt
    participant R as router.sh (C4)
    participant T as mcp_retrieve.py (C5)
    participant C as cognee (C6 / sse)
    participant M as msdocs (http)
    participant G as github (http)
    participant L as Claude model

    U->>R: UserPromptSubmit injects prompt text
    R->>R: classify_domains() + gate
    R->>R: github gate = concrete entity only
    R-->>L: if no domain matched, inject nothing and exit
    R->>T: if matched, start retrieval fan-out
    T->>C: retrieve cognee search for eposforge
    C-->>T: graph chunks
    T->>M: retrieve microsoft_docs_search
    M-->>T: doc chunks
    T->>G: retrieve search_code or search_issues
    G-->>T: code or issue hits
    T-->>R: return results with per-adapter timeout and fail-open
    R->>R: label and truncate with per-source and global caps
    R-->>L: inject context blocks from cognee, msdocs, and github
    L->>L: respond using pre-injected context
